.TH DELPHI-CROP 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
crop \- Crop an image to a social media aspect ratio
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcrop\fR [\fB\-\-ratio\fR] [\fB\-\-position\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIIMAGES\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Crop an image to a social media aspect ratio
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-ratio\fR \fI<RATIO>\fR [default: 1:1]
Aspect ratio (e.g. 1:1, 4:5, 16:9)
.TP
\fB\-\-position\fR \fI<POSITION>\fR [default: center]
Crop position: center, top, bottom, left, right, top\-left, top\-right, bottom\-left, bottom\-right
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIIMAGES\fR]
Input image(s)
